Star Wars: Dark Disciple

:: Type: Audio book (unabridged) + mobi/epub

:: Author: Christie Golden

:: Voice: Marc Thompson

:: Summary:

   In the war for control of the galaxy between the
   armies of the dark side and the Republic, former
   Jedi Master turned ruthless Sith Lord Count Dooku
   has grown ever more brutal in his tactics.
   
   And when he orders the massacre of helpless refugees,
   the Jedi Council can see no alternative but to take
   drastic action: targeting the Empire's most cold—blooded
   disciple for assassination.
   
   But Dooku is dangerous prey, so the Council decides
   to bring both sides of the Force to bear - teaming
   brash Jedi Knight Quinlan Vos with infamous ex-Sith
   acolyte Asajj Ventress....
